Create a new directory for your project:
--> mkdir book-management-api
--> cd book-management-api


Initialize a new Node.js project:
--> npm init -y

Install express for REST API, body-parser for parsing and mysql for interacting with db:
--> npm install express mysql body-parser


npm install mysql exoress bcryptjs jsonwebtoken body-parser
(npm install) --> for all npm installations

npm start 
   OR 
node app.js
   OR
npm i -g nodemon
nodemon app.js